  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add chopped garlic and saut\u00e9 until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add fenugreek leaves and cook for another 2-3 minutes until softened but still crisp.",
    "Stir in lemon juice and salt to taste. Remove from heat immediately to prevent the leaves from becoming too soft or bitter.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh parsley."
